============================================================
      nuEI: An interface for a neutrino event in nuCD
============================================================


Dependencies
------------
- ROOT version 5.34 or newer
- Scons version 1.0.0 or newer (to compile and build library [http://www.scons.org/])
- Python version 1.5.2 or newer(Scons dependency)

Installation
------------

In order to build nuEI just type:

scons install

or, if you prefer to install it in some folder of your choice:

scons PREFIX=/path/to/installation/folder install

The building creates an nuei-config file in the bin directory under the installation path. Make sure you add
/path/to/installation/folder/bin to your $PATH variable and then check your installation by doing

nuei-config
